&lt;li&gt;$ wget &lt;a href=&quot;http://download.redis.io/releases/redis-3.2.2.tar.gz&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;http://download.redis.io/releases/redis-3.2.2.tar.gz&lt;/a&gt;
    
